 B550M PLUS2 WIFI 版</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>固态 三星 980 1T</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>内存 芝奇黄金戟 DDR4 4000 16G*2</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>电源 海韵 FOCUS GX750</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>风扇 爱国者 ARGB 三联装</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>618 折后总价：5652 ￥</p>\n","last_modified":1654832860,"replies":8,"id":858668},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f61d/6947/375_large.png?m=1650095232","name":"go","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f61d/6947/375_normal.png?m=1650095232","title":"Go 编程语言","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/go","topics":2309,"footer":"","header":"Go 是一个开源的编程语言，它能让构造简单、可靠且高效的软件变得容易。","title_alternative":"The Go Programming Language","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f61d/6947/375_mini.png?m=1650095232","stars":3204,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":375,"parent_node_name":"programming"},"member":{"id":506458,"username":"daokedao","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/daokedao","website":"http://www.xoolee.com","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5db566896813254bd15c69aebc14a9bf?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5db566896813254bd15c69aebc14a9bf?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5db566896813254bd15c69aebc14a9bf?s=73&d=retro","created":1599092182,"last_modified":1654830458},"last_reply_by":"pathletboy","last_touched":1654837745,"title":"Go 的 http 服务器，同时下载的连接不能超过两个吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/858651","created":1654830728,"deleted":0,"content":"一个最简单的 http 服务器：\r\n\r\n```go\r\nfunc main() {\r\n\tfs := http.FileServer( http.Dir(\"./public\"))\r\n\thttp.Handle(\"/\", fs)\r\n\thttp.ListenAndServe(\":8888\", nil)\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n用 curl 测试几个连接同时下载：\r\n```\r\ncurl --limit-rate 1k http://1.2.3.4:9999/file.zip --output NUL\r\n```\r\n\r\n结果是，只有第一个和第二个连接正常下载，其他的连接处于停滞状态，只有前面的连接下载完了，后面的才能接着下载。\r\n\r\n如果把服务器换成 nginx 则多个连接都可以同时下载。\r\n\r\n以上都是在 Windows 11 下进行的\r\nGo 的版本是 1.18.1","content_rendered":"<p>一个最简单的 http 服务器：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-go\">func main() {\n\tfs := http.FileServer( http.Dir(\"./public\"))\n\thttp.Handle(\"/\", fs)\n\thttp.ListenAndServe(\":8888\", nil)\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>用 curl 测试几个连接同时下载：</p>\n<pre><code>curl --limit-rate 1k http://1.2.3.4:9999/file.zip --output NUL\n</code></pre>\n<p>结果是，只有第一个和第二个连接正常下载，其他的连接处于停滞状态，只有前面的连接下载完了，后面的才能接着下载。</p>\n<p>如果把服务器换成 nginx 则多个连接都可以同时下载。</p>\n<p>以上都是在 Windows 11 下进行的\nGo 的版本是 1.18.1</p>\n","last_modified":1654830728,"replies":8,"id":858651},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":18659,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2186,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":395483,"username":"PYHII","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/PYHII","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d843/c108/395483_mini.png?m=1629121533","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d843/c108/395483_normal.png?m=1629121533","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d843/c108/395483_large.png?m=1629121533","created":1553593991,"last_modified":1629121533},"last_reply_by":"Xusually","last_touched":1654824625,"title":"关于 MacBook Pro 17 120g 硬盘扩容的问题。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/858599","created":1654822338,"deleted":0,"content":"现在有两种方案\r\n1 、淘宝买一个接口，可以替换原来的硬盘来扩容；好处是不需要随时带一块硬盘，坏处是破坏了电脑原来的硬件。\r\n2 、外接一个移动硬盘。把系统安装到这个硬盘里面运行双系统，但是会有点不方便。\r\n\r\n目前打算用第二种方案。\r\n\r\n请问 type-c 的接口 usd3.x 和雷电 有什么区别吗？对以后运行的数据读写又什么影响吗？\r\n还有买什么牌子的好一点，","content_rendered":"<p>现在有两种方案\n1 、淘宝买一个接口，可以替换原来的硬盘来扩容；好处是不需要随时带一块硬盘，坏处是破坏了电脑原来的硬件。\n2 、外接一个移动硬盘。把系统安装到这个硬盘里面运行双系统，但是会有点不方便。</p>\n<p>目前打算用第二种方案。</p>\n<p>请问 type-c 的接口 usd3.x 和雷电 有什么区别吗？对以后运行的数据读写又什么影响吗？\n还有买什么牌子的好一点，</p>\n","last_modified":1654822338,"replies":8,"id":858599},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1651385949","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1651385949","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":49179,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1651385949","stars":7850,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":316580,"username":"jwenjian","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/jwenjian","website":"https://1link.fun","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"jwenjian","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b810/a0da/316580_mini.png?m=1646955951","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b810/a0da/316580_normal.png?m=1646955951","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b810/a0da/316580_large.png?m=1646955951","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b810/a0da/316580_xlarge.png?m=1646955951","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b810/a0da/316580_xlarge.png?m=1646955951","avatar_xxxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b810/a0da/316580_xlarge.png?m=1646955951","created":1526375839,"last_modified":1646955951},"last_reply_by":"Tokin","last_touched":1654825538,"title":"GitHub 开始测试成就系统（beta）","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/858595","created":1654821498,"deleted":0,"content":"刷 HN 看到的新闻， 你在 GitHub 上的活动会触发一些成就，然后这些成就的徽章就会显示在你的个人主页上。\r\n\r\n至于都有哪些成就徽章， 以及这些徽章如何获得，保密， 全都靠自己探索。\r\n\r\n之前的代码保存计划算是其中一个，我刚才收到了另外一个， 就是当你有 PR 被 merge ， 会收到一个 Pull Shark 的徽章。\r\n\r\n\r\n![]( https://s2.loli.net/2022/06/10/MDvAhZHk1ucaxpJ.png)\r\n\r\n